# Simple MicroIR example for BinRevX

func sum_to_ten entry entry
block entry
assign i const 0
assign sum const 0
term jump hdr
block hdr
term branch lt i 10 body exit
block body
assign sum binop add sum i
assign i binop add i 1
term jump hdr
block exit
term ret sum
endfunc

func branch_only entry entry
block entry
term branch eq x 0 then0 else0
block then0
assign r const 1
term jump join
block else0
assign r const 2
term jump join
block join
term ret r
endfunc
